data.meta_description:
amadour_ on April 8, 2022: "Playing piano for friends in Mexico City. Song and lyrics by yours truly.

Lyrics:

The season before grapes ripen,
Your eyes make the way to my mouth,
And now the shadow clouds on pages,
You were so inviting…

Dropped from the great of memories,
How I love you so.

The season before grapes ripen,
Your eyes make the way to my mouth,
And now the shadow of clouds on pages…

“The Season Before Grapes Ripen” by Amadour

#piano #amadour #jazzmusic".
